data.description: Make this home your own fairy tale in Sherwood Forest! Full brick ranch with 3 LARGE bedrooms situated on nice sized lot. Just under 2,000 finished square feet. Major items have been done for you- Furnace and A/C 2024, All Windows Replaced 2024, Hot water Heater 2023, Flooring 2018. Put your own finishing touches on the rest! Bedrooms have large closets for extra storage. HUGE backyard! Selling AS-IS.
